                        <note>The introduction to the Pauline Epistles begins with
                           <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምክንያተ፡ ጽሒፎቱ፡ መልእክተ፡</foreign>, listing the reasons and circumstances of the writing of the Epistles.</note>
